Clarification Notice

References to coherence, bands, or related terminology within this repository are descriptive rather than prescriptive. They do not imply certification, endorsement, or compliance.

This work describes structural conditions of stability in bounded systems. It does not impose governance, guarantee safety, or enforce ethical standards.

